Package: riab
Type: Package
Title: Multi-Scale Assessments of Spatial Model Accuracy
Version: 0.1.0
Author: person("Michael", "Mahoney", , "mike.mahoney.218@gmail.com", 
        role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-2402-304X"))
Description: Functions aiding in multi-scale assessments of spatial model 
    accuracy. By reporting spatially-explicit accuracy for predictions 
    aggregated at multiple scales, users are able to provide more useful 
    descriptions of how effectively their models represent the areas model
    consumers care about.
